Example application written with Rapid
======================================

To run:

  $: java -server -Xms50m -Xmx50m -jar rapid-examples-1.0-SNAPSHOT-allinone.jar --listenAddress "127.0.0.1:1234" --seedAddress "127.0.0.1:1234" --akkaAddress "127.0.0.1:2534" --role "starter"

... and from another terminal:

  $: java -server -Xms50m -Xmx50m -jar rapid-examples-1.0-SNAPSHOT-allinone.jar --listenAddress "127.0.0.1:1235" --seedAddress "127.0.0.1:1234" --akkaAddress "127.0.0.1:2535" --role "joiner"
